data.description: Nestled on a quiet dead-end street with minimal traffic, this exceptional property boasts a plethora of desirable features that make it an ideal home. With generously sized rooms and well-appointed bathrooms, there is ample space. Even a flex room that could be turned into a hidden pantry! But thats not all - the standout feature of this property is the large, heated 3,121 sq ft shop and the 382 sq ft covered utility area. With a driveway from Cottage ave, straight to Climax ave! Imagine having dedicated space to pursue your hobbies or turn your entrepreneurial dreams to reality... or atleast not have to manuever that large RV so many times to park. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property yours.  Experience the blend of convenience and endless possibilities!
